Comparison of localized sea-level rise projections for Norfolk, VA. Panels from left to right are projected with higher emissions scenarios (increasing in shade) and panels from top to bottom increase in time from 2030 to 2100. “FD” refers to fast Antarctic ice sheet dynamics and blocks depict the 5, 25, 50, 75, and 95% quantiles for Sweet et al.
